<table>
  <tr>
<td height="28" align="center" background="Images/Tool_bar1.jpg" style="background-repeat:no-repeat">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;     <strong>&nbsp;<font color="#FFFFFF">H&#432;&#7899;ng d&#7851;n mua h&agrave;ng</font></strong></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="color:#07b8fa"><div align="justify"><b>1) Duy&#7879;t v&agrave; ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m </b></div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">H&agrave;ng ho&aacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&acirc;n theo t&#7915;ng h&atilde;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t hay ki&#7875;u d&aacute;ng c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m,... </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">Duy&#7879;t xem h&agrave;ng ho&aacute; trong t&#7915;ng ch&#7911; &#273;&#7875; ch&iacute;nh, click v&agrave;o h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh hay t&ecirc;n c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7875; xem chi ti&#7871;t s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">B&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&ocirc;ng c&#7909; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7883; nhanh ch&oacute;ng h&agrave;ng ho&aacute; m&agrave; b&#7841;n c&#7847;n t&igrave;m (h&#7895; tr&#7907; t&igrave;m ki&#7871;m ti&#7871;ng Vi&#7879;t v&#7899;i chu&#7849;n Unicode). Ho&#7863;c b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7883; nhanh c&aacute;c ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873; b&#7841;n &#273;ang quan t&acirc;m b&#7857;ng c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t &#7903;   menu  b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i    (menu ch&#7911; &#273;&#7873;). B&#7841;n c&#361;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; li&#7879;t k&ecirc; c&aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a nh&agrave; xu&#7845;t b&#7843;n hay t&aacute;c gi&#7843; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch click v&agrave;o c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t nh&agrave; xu&#7845;t b&#7843;n hay t&ecirc;n t&aacute;c gi&#7843; c&#7911;a m&#7895;i t&aacute;c ph&#7849;m.</div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="color:#07b8fa"><div align="justify"><b>2) Th&ecirc;m s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m v&agrave;o gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n:</b> </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">Trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh duy&#7879;t s&#7843;n v&agrave; ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, n&#7871;u b&#7841;n mu&#7889;n mua s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&agrave;o th&igrave; click v&agrave;o n&uacute;t &quot;Mua&quot; &#273;&#7875; th&ecirc;m s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&oacute; v&agrave;o gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh. </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">Sau khi nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t &quot;Mua&quot; h&#7879; th&#7889;ng s&#7869; chuy&#7875;n b&#7841;n &#273;&#7871;n gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. N&#7871;u mu&#7889;n ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c mua th&ecirc;m s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m kh&aacute;c, b&#7841;n nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o n&uacute;t ti&#7871;p &quot;Ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c &quot;                      , n&#7871;u mu&#7889;n thanh to&aacute;n b&#7841;n nh&#7845;n v&agrave;o m&uacute;t &quot;Thanh to&aacute;n&quot;. &#272;&#7891;ng th&#7901;i l&uacute;c n&agrave;y b&#7841;n s&#7869; th&#7845;y t&#7893;ng tr&#7883; gi&aacute; h&agrave;ng ho&aacute; trong gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a m&igrave;nh tr&ecirc;n gi&#7887; &#7903; g&oacute;c ph&#7843;i tr&ecirc;n c&#7911;a m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; click v&agrave;o &#273;&oacute; &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7871;n trang gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng.</div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="color:#07b8fa"><div align="justify"><b>3) C&aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c thanh to&aacute;n:</b></div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="color:#07b8fa"><div align="justify"><em>B&#432;&#7899;c 1 - Xem th&ocirc;ng tin gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng:</em> </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">H&#7879; th&#7889;ng hi&#7875;n th&#7883; c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#7863;t mua nh&#432; ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i, &#273;&#417;n gi&aacute;, s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng, gi&aacute; tr&#7883;... T&#7841;i &#273;&acirc;y b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; thay &#273;&#7893;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng h&agrave;ng ho&aacute; b&#7857;ng c&aacute;ch nh&#7853;p v&agrave;o s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng trong &ocirc; &quot;S&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng &quot;. N&#7871;u mu&#7889;n tr&#7843; l&#7841;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m (kh&ocirc;ng mua n&#7919;a), b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n v&agrave;o bi&#7875;u t&#432;&#7907;ng th&ugrave;ng r&aacute;c &#7903; &#273;&#7847;u d&ograve;ng c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7875; xo&aacute; n&oacute; ra kh&#7887;i gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n. Click v&agrave;o &quot;Thanh to&aacute;n&quot; &#273;&#7875; sang b&#432;&#7899;c k&#7871; ti&#7871;p. </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">N&#7871;u &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p r&#7891;i th&igrave; b&#7841;n s&#7869; chuy&#7875;n sang b&#432;&#7899;c 2, n&#7871;u ch&#432;a &#273;&#259;ng nnh&#7853;p h&#7879; th&#7889;ng s&#7869; y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u b&#7841;n &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p tr&#432;&#7899;c khi thanh to&aacute;n. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; l&agrave;m th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n v&#7899;i BaoHan shop th&igrave; b&#7841;n &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p v&#7899;i t&ecirc;n &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p v&agrave; m&#7853;t kh&#7849;u &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;, n&#7871;u ch&#432;a b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; &#7903; b&#432;&#7899;c n&agrave;y. Xin l&#432;u &yacute; r&#7857;ng, &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p v&agrave;o BaoHan shop b&#7841;n c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i cung c&#7845;p c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin sau: </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">- T&ecirc;n &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p: m&agrave; b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; l&agrave;m th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n.    V&igrave; m&#7885;i giao d&#7883;ch mua b&aacute;n ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i s&#7869; li&ecirc;n h&#7879; qua email m&agrave; b&#7841;n cung c&#7845;p khi &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; l&agrave;m th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n. </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">- M&#7853;t kh&#7849;u &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p: l&agrave; m&#7853;t kh&#7849;u b&#7841;n &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; v&agrave;o BaoHan shop. </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="color:#07b8fa"><div align="justify">B&#432;&#7899;c 2 - C&aacute;ch th&#7913;c thanh to&aacute;n v&agrave; giao h&agrave;ng: </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">
      <p>Nh&#7853;p v&agrave;o c&aacute;ch th&#7913;c thanh to&aacute;n v&agrave; &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881; giao h&agrave;ng. </p>
      <p><a href="?mnu=huongdan_ttvc" class="menu2">Xem th&ecirc;m</a></p>
    </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="color:#07b8fa"><div align="justify">B&#432;&#7899;c 3 - X&aacute;c nh&#7853;n mua h&agrave;ng: </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">B&#7841;n h&atilde;y ki&#7875;m tra th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7863;t mua tr&#432;&#7899;c b&#432;&#7899;c n&agrave;y. N&#7871;u &#273;&#7891;ng &yacute; b&#7841;n click &quot;&#272;&#7863;t mua h&agrave;ng &quot;. </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="color:#07b8fa"><div align="justify">B&#432;&#7899;c 4 - K&#7871;t th&uacute;c: </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><div align="justify">H&#7879; th&#7889;ng s&#7869; l&#432;u l&#7841;i th&ocirc;ng tin &#273;&#417;n h&agrave;ng c&#7911;a b&#7841;n v&agrave; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a BaoHan shop s&#7869; li&ecirc;n h&#7879; v&#7899;i b&#7841;n &#273;&#7875; giao                    h&agrave;ng theo y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u. </div></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>&nbsp;</td>
  </tr>
</table>


